      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ULTIMATE WEAPON NZ (3) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 3.5 metres from a handy winner in third at Menangle. Likely to get all the favours from this lower draw. Can find winning ways. DANIBOY (5) spanked his rivals in a maiden win at this circuit and distance three back and has been runner-up in both tries since, missing narrowly here last start. Go well again. SHAZADELE (11) only beat one home last start at Menangle last start but the form at this venue prior to that had been good with a string of wins or placings. May just need a bit of luck from this draw but was runner-up from a similar barrier two back. INDASKY NZ (10) draws on the back row but cannot be left out after recording a sequence of top-three finishes.",
